{"tid":1923641,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"《行動POST》10秒剿滅CCTVB大法","createTime":"2020-03-13T07:47:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T12:42:05.000Z","uid":345840,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d11475b26bc775d482b07b773577b7ccc18df0e9","tid":1923641,"uid":345840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:47:13.000Z","msg":"港共係香港有一文一武兩大打手<br />\n即係血腥鎮壓的黑警同專門維穩的CCTVB<br />\n既然香港黑警個PAGE 4日谷到38萬FANS<br />\n我地無理由放過包庇黑警暴行的CCTVB唔做野<br />\n而且方法只需要抽10秒出黎做<br />\n<br />\n同我LIKE左《抵制tvb戰線 - 杯葛廣告商》佢<br />\n同我LIKE左《抵制tvb戰線 - 杯葛廣告商》佢<br />\n同我LIKE左《抵制tvb戰線 - 杯葛廣告商》佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb%2F&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=d95f9d3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/</a><br />\n<br />\n自TVB戰線7月開始之後，大家可能唔知破壞力幾驚人：<br />\n&mdash;過百品牌同TVB割蓆，撤走TVB廣告<br />\n&mdash;TVB廣告成為品牌毒藥，Agency 向Inhouse sell TVB廣告會俾客屌<br />\n&mdash;TVB由盈轉虧，舊年埋單至少蝕2億以上，要炒成10%員工填數<br />\n&mdash;董事局主席陳國強蝕到賣股唔玩辭職走佬<br />\n&mdash;股價由去年高位大跌近40%，再融資想吊命都面對困難<br />\n<br />\n如果抵制TVB個PAGE可以同香港黑警一樣有38萬LIKE<br />\n代表每個落廣告俾TVB的品牌都要同38萬人割蓆<br />\n都足夠嚇到D品牌尻縮<br />\n<br />\n如果係懶，LIKE左個PAGE佢同SET埋「搶先看」，咁就夠<br />\n如果有心，可以同FD吹水時傾起，順便叫埋佢地一齊LIKE<br />\n如果得閒，做埋每日任送TVB一程<br />\n不過無論如何，我P牌自推唔到<br />\n行動POST請幫推！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n利申:尋日貼時事台秒沉，所以係創意台貼多次，希望大家幫幫手"},{"pid":"7e43f3aa21c0f260803a8b31e34fc8599b073f1f","tid":1923641,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3937fc718f198e40da3b46dfd6c2e8011514c5","tid":1923641,"uid":34449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:48:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dcbff48006b1bcda6ef084889da00172b9d0ec76","tid":1923641,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:48:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58ac68fd6cd130ce6671eda928aa731dcb35963","tid":1923641,"uid":147895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:48:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3aa4f08fe7996d7d7d346cc005b335cc0e5d590","tid":1923641,"uid":187987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:48:53.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"0860022b69333b2632cb2c37eeba41d088322776","tid":1923641,"uid":345840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:51:01.000Z","msg":"我係MARKETING人<br />\n行內人做野真係好簡單<br />\n落廣告就係評估對銷售有無效益同風險<br />\n<br />\n當TVB戰線有幾十萬人FOLLOW的話<br />\n撥預算落廣告果時，係無法解釋風險果PART<br />\n所以，要參與TVB戰線的話，<br />\n唔止做每日任務幫到手<br />\n甚至齋搵到人LIKE個PAGE<br />\n其實已經好幫到手<br />\n希望大家都一齊用10秒幫拖，THX"},{"pid":"3f37bdd6d0d5e6761f0b60ffcb326f7a52f91d14","tid":1923641,"uid":345840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:52:17.000Z","msg":"多謝各位手足幫推"},{"pid":"d76368e14e9dd451d90e077b9aa294902bebc2f3","tid":1923641,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T08:25:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8903ecf06f314ff98ae44d79266d6b5926d32129","tid":1923641,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:02:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"9bcf9197ac01f7ec137cb6221bbaed6d670fee99","tid":1923641,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:08:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2a8d89d3c830b582025118b08d5f0d5f873f12","tid":1923641,"uid":17646,"like":0,